# Version Bumping

When bumping the Nunus version number, always update **all three** locations:

1. **`manifest.json`** — the `"version"` field
2. **`safari/NunusSafari.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj`** — all `MARKETING_VERSION` entries
3. **`safari/scripts/gen_pbxproj.py`** — all `MARKETING_VERSION` entries

All three must stay in sync.

Each release also increments **`CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION`** in `project.pbxproj` and `gen_pbxproj.py` (Apple build number).

## Release levels

- **MAJOR** — newly supported publication in `manifest.json`, or breaking changes
- **MINOR** — improvements within publications already shipped (default `./scripts/release.sh` bump)
- **PATCH** — bug fixes only (not used by release automation today)

## Agent edits

When the agent changes committable files in a turn, bump **patch** per **agent-patch-version** (always-applied rule). Use `./scripts/bump-version.py --version X.Y.Z` after other edits.
